すべてのクラス

  • クラスの概要 
    クラス 説明
    Author
    The Author class represents an Author of an embedded message.
    DiscordWebHook
    Definity's DiscordWebhook allows for easy message sending to your Servers through a webhook!
    DiscordWebHook.Builder
    The Builder class is used to easily build DiscordWebHook Objects.
    Embed
    The Embed class represents an Embedded Message that can be send with a DiscordWebHook message.
    Embed.Builder
    The Builder class allows for easy creation of an Embed Object.
    Field
    The Field class represents a field in an embedded message.
    Footer
    The Footer class represents the footer of an embedded message.
    Image
    The Image class represents an image in your embedded message.
    Thumbnail
    The Thumbnail class represents a Thumbnail in your embedded message.
    Utils
    The Utils class contains important methods that we use across our project.
